---
import "../../styles/home/home.css";
---

<section id="services" class="services-section section-padding">
  <div class="section-title title-right">
    <h1>My Services</h1>
    <div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-cards grid-3-2">
    <div class="service-card card-dark" id="service-card">
      <img
        src="/assets//Icons/create-wordpress-business-website.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">WordPress Business Websites</h2>
      <p class="service-card-des">
        Mobile-first, SEO-ready websites built fast. Easy to edit
        (Elementor/Gutenberg), optimized for speed, and set up with clear
        contact paths (email, WhatsApp, forms). Perfect for small businesses in
        Sri Lanka and worldwide.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="Responsive WordPress business website on laptop and phone"> -->
    </div>
    <div class="service-card card-dark">
      <img
        src="/assets//Icons/e-commerce-store-wordpress-website-create.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">WooCommerce Online Stores</h2>
      <p class="service-card-des">
        Start selling with a secure, simple store. Product management, coupons,
        shipping rules, and modern checkout. Integrates with popular payment
        gateways and analytics so you can see what’s working.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="WooCommerce product grid and checkout UI"> -->
    </div>
    <div class="service-card card-dark">
      <img
        src="/assets//Icons/online-resume-and-portfolio-website-design-wordpress.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">Portfolio Websites for Creatives</h2>
      <p class="service-card-des">
        Clean, fast portfolios for photographers, designers, and artists.
        Beautiful galleries, lightbox viewing, simple pricing sections, and easy
        inquiry forms, so clients can book you without friction.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="WordPress photography portfolio gallery with lightbox"> -->
    </div>
    <div class="service-card card-dark">
      <img
        src="/assets/Icons/landing-page-design-wordpress.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">Landing Page Design</h2>
      <p>
        funnels tailored for ads or campaigns. Clear messaging, fast load,
        persuasive layout, and action-focused CTAs. Built to capture leads with
        minimal distractions.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="Minimal landing page with bold headline and CTA"> -->
    </div>
    <div class="service-card card-dark">
      <img
        src="/assets/Icons/wordpress-website-maintainence.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">WordPress Care & Maintenance</h2>
      <p>
        Stay worry-free with updates, backups, uptime monitoring, and security
        checks. Includes minor content edits and speed tune-ups to keep things
        smooth after launch.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="WordPress maintenance dashboard with updates and backups."> -->
    </div>
    <div class="service-card card-dark">
      <img
        src="/assets/Icons/wordpress-website-seo.png"
        alt="service-card-icon"
      />
      <h2 class="service-card-title">SEO Setup & Speed Boost</h2>
      <p>
        Technical basics done right: on-page SEO, metadata, schema, image
        optimization, and Core Web Vitals improvements. Clear audit + quick wins
        to help you rank and load faster.
      </p>
      <!-- <img src="service-img/" alt="Website performance scores and SEO snippet preview."> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="./../../js/home/serviceSection.js"></script>
